WEBVTT

1
01:18:13.250 --> 01:18:15.960 
但我总感觉这对我很重要
but I thought maybe it was important...

2
01:18:16.050 --> 01:18:16.950 
- 你的羊
Your sheep!

3
01:18:17.120 --> 01:18:18.040 
- 我的羊
My sheep?

4
01:18:20.070 --> 01:18:21.010 
什么意思
I don't get it.

5
01:18:21.320 --> 01:18:23.000 
这是飞行员给你的
The Aviator gave it to you

6
01:18:23.080 --> 01:18:25.940 
在地球上的沙漠里，是为了处理红面包树
in the desert on Earth, to eat the baobabs.

7
01:18:26.160 --> 01:18:28.270 
- 大祸临头 - 大祸临头
- Catastrophe. - Catastrophe.

8
01:18:28.660 --> 01:18:29.560 
没错
That's right.

9
01:18:29.790 --> 01:18:31.950 
这些都是飞行员画给你的
The Aviator drew all of these for you.

10
01:18:32.370 --> 01:18:36.590 
- 他现在非常需要你 - 我？ 他需要我？
- He really needs you right now. - Me? He needs me?

11
01:18:39.600 --> 01:18:43.520 
真正的问题不在于长大，在于遗忘
Growing up is not the problem. Forgetting is.

